✅ 1. OpenAI Authentication Error

Error message

openai.AuthenticationError: No API key provided

✔ Fix

import os
os.environ["OPENAI_API_KEY"] = "your_api_key"

from openai import OpenAI
client = OpenAI(api_key=os.environ["OPENAI_API_KEY"])


---

✅ 2. OpenAI "Bad Request" / 400 Error

This happens when your prompt is too long or you send wrong JSON.

Fix

Use correct structure:

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="gpt-4o-mini",
    messages=[{"role":"user","content":user_input}]
)


---

✅ 3. Altair Renderer Error (MOST COMMON in Colab)

Error

RendererError: No such renderer: colab

✔ Fix

Add this BEFORE any altair chart:

import altair as alt
alt.renderers.enable('default')

Or for PNG rendering:

alt.renderers.set_embed_options(scaleFactor=2)


---

✅ 4. Gradio "Port already in use" Error

Error

Address already in use: 7860

✔ Fix

Kill previous Gradio processes:

!fuser -k 7860/tcp

Then launch:

demo.launch(share=True)


---

✅ 5. ngrok not working (Tunnel not found)

Error

Tunnel 404 / ngrok stopped / connection refused

✔ Fix

Reconnect ngrok:

from pyngrok import ngrok
ngrok.kill()       # IMPORTANT
public_url = ngrok.connect(7860)
public_url


---

✅ 6. Colab Crashing / 504 Gateway Timeout

Caused by:

long-running OpenAI calls

Colab sleeping

cell execution stopping


✔ Fix

Keep server alive:

while True:
  pass

Or use:

demo.launch(share=True, server_port=7860)


---

✅ 7. Missing Folder Error ("No such file or directory")

Error

FileNotFoundError: ./agents not found

✔ Fix

Create folders:

import os
os.makedirs("agents", exist_ok=True)
os.makedirs("assets", exist_ok=True)


---

✅ 8. JSON Decode Error

Error

JSONDecodeError: Expecting value

Usually because OpenAI output isn’t in JSON.

✔ Fix

Force JSON format:

messages=[
  {"role":"system","content":"Return ONLY valid JSON"},
  {"role":"user","content":prompt}
]


---

✅ 9. Import Errors (common in Colab)

Error

ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'python-dotenv'

✔ Fix

Install missing modules:

!pip install python-dotenv altair openai gradio pyngrok


---

✅ 10. Rate Limit Error (OpenAI)

Error

RateLimitError: You exceeded your quota

✔ Fix

Add exponential retry:

import time

def retry_openai(fn):
    for i in range(5):
        try:
            return fn()
        except:
            time.sleep(2*(i+1))
            
✅ 11. GRADIO — Common Problems & Fixes


---

❌ Problem 1: ImportError: No module named gradio

✔ Fix

!pip install gradio


---

❌ Problem 2: “Port 7860 already in use”

✔ Fix

!fuser -k 7860/tcp


---

❌ Problem 3: Gradio UI shows blank page / not loading

✔ Fix

demo.launch(share=True, server_name="0.0.0.0", server_port=7860)


---

❌ Problem 4: Gradio UI stuck at “Running…”

✔ Fix Make sure last cell is not running infinite loops or using input().


---

❌ Problem 5: "404 ngrok tunnel not found"

✔ Fix

from pyngrok import ngrok
ngrok.kill()
ngrok.connect(7860)


---


---

✅ 12. OPENAI — Common Problems & Fixes


---

❌ Problem 1: AuthenticationError: No API key provided

✔ Fix

import os
os.environ["OPENAI_API_KEY"] = "your_api_key"


---

❌ Problem 2: “Bad Request / 400 Error”

Usually because of wrong message format.

✔ Fix

from openai import OpenAI
client = OpenAI()

chat = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="gpt-4o-mini",
    messages=[{"role":"user","content":"Hello"}]
)


---

❌ Problem 3: "No such model"

✔ Fix Use latest models:

gpt-4o-mini
gpt-4o
gpt-4.1


---

❌ Problem 4: "Rate limit exceeded"

✔ Fix

import time

def retry(fn):
    for i in range(5):
        try:
            return fn()
        except:
            time.sleep(2*(i+1))


---


---

✅13. ALTAIR — Common Problems & Fixes


---

❌ Problem 1: Renderer Error

RendererError: No such renderer: colab

✔ Fix

import altair as alt
alt.renderers.enable('default')


---

❌ Problem 2: ImportError: cannot import name TopLevelSpec

This happens when Altair and Vegafusion version mismatch.

✔ Fix

!pip install -U altair vegafusion


---

❌ Problem 3: Altair chart not showing in Colab

✔ Fix

alt.renderers.set_embed_options(actions=False)


---


---

✅ 14. WHISPER — Common Problems & Fixes


---

❌ Problem 1: whisper module not found

✔ Fix

!pip install -U openai-whisper


---

❌ Problem 2: Torch not installed

✔ Fix

!pip install torch torchvision torchaudio


---

❌ Problem 3: Slow transcription in Colab

✔ Fix Force FP16:

import whisper
model = whisper.load_model("small", device="cuda")


---

❌ Problem 4: CUDA not available

✔ Fix Use CPU:

model = whisper.load_model("base", device="cpu")


---


---

✅ 15. NUMPY — Common Problems & Fixes


---

❌ Problem 1: "Numpy version mismatch"

Happens when installing Whisper or Altair.

✔ Fix

!pip install --upgrade numpy


---

❌ Problem 2: ImportError after upgrade

✔ Fix Restart kernel:

Runtime → Restart runtime


---

❌ Problem 3: Numpy showing strange warnings

✔ Fix

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')